title: 'Boys and Girl - Week 2 Atlanta Thriller Reaction; 20 Early Season Cowboys Questions

description:
On today’s episode of the 'Boys and Girl Podcast, Jane is off, but Laurie Horesh from ESPN Australia joins Bobby to chat Cowboys. They talk about the thrilling victory over Atlanta, and play 20 questions to evaluate where the Cowboys stand. Follow Jane and Bobby on Twitter and subscribe to get all the latest inside information from two of the most connected people in the Cowboys’ community.
